# Increments::Schedule

Find out our special remote days and eagerly wait for them!

## Installation

Add this line to your application's Gemfile:

```ruby
gem 'increments-schedule'
```

And then execute:

```bash
$ bundle
```

Or install it yourself as:

```bash
$ gem install increments-schedule
```

